},\n    {\n      \"id\": \"47eb9367-a34b-433e-9bb6-fb45424543cd\",\n      \"agentId\": \"ireneo\",\n      \"name\": \"Vitrine Funes (SEO Daily)\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1771263495286,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1771309460703,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"0 9 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run this exact command to trigger the Vitrine agent via Jules (do not change anything, just run it):\\n\\nexport JULES_API_KEY=$(grep JULES_API_KEY /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/secrets.env | cut -d= -f2)\\n\\npython3 /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/ireneo/workspace/skills/jules-api/jules_client.py create-session \\\\\\n  --source \\\"sources/github/franklinbaldo/funes-memories\\\" \\\\\\n  --title \\\"🪟 Vitrine: Daily SEO Scan\\\" \\\\\\n  --prompt \\\"$(cat /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/ireneo/workspace/memory/bank/jules-agents/vitrine-funes.md)\\\"\\n\\nReport the output JSON (Session ID).\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1771318800000\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"9e99a605-48d8-4f5a-bde3-67cdeb8fff4e\",\n      \"agentId\": \"aparicio\",\n      \"name\": \"Triagem de PRs do Jules (fork → repo original)\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1771204172004,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1771312173244,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 7200000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1771204172004\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"TAREFA: Triagem automática de PRs do Jules no fork do Franklin.\\n\\n1. Rode `gh pr list --repo franklinbaldo/adibaldo.github.io --json number,title,state,createdAt` para listar PRs abertas.\\n2. Se não houver PRs abertas, responda apenas 'Nenhuma PR nova.' e encerre.\\n3. Para cada PR aberta:\\n   a. Rode `gh pr diff <number> --repo franklinbaldo/adibaldo.github.io` para pegar o diff.\\n   b. Analise o diff contra o checklist em memory/diretrizes-editoriais.md seção 4.1.\\n   c. CRITÉRIOS RÍGIDOS:\\n      - Tecedor/Vitrine/Farol (SEO, links, metadados): geralmente OK, mas verificar se não mexem em texto narrativo.\\n      - Veritas (fact-check): REJEITAR se inserir parágrafos novos na prosa do Adi. Só aprovar notas/disclaimers.\\n      - Prosa: NUNCA aprovar edições no miolo narrativo do Adi.\\n      - Tags/description/frontmatter: OK se respeitam a voz original.\\n   d. Se APROVADA: clone o repo original, faça merge da branch (sem force push), push, e feche a PR no fork.\\n   e. Se REJEITADA: deixe aberta e anote o motivo.\\n4. Ao final, envie um resumo ao Franklin dizendo o que foi mergeado e o que foi rejeitado, com os motivos.\",\n        \"model\": \"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1771319372004,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1771312172031,\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 1213,\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 14,\n        \"lastError\": \"Error: All models failed (2): anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5: No API key found for provider \\\"anthropic\\\". Auth store: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json (agentDir: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent). Configure auth for this agent (openclaw agents add <id>) or copy auth-profiles.json from the main agentDir. (auth) | google/gemini-3-flash-preview: No API key found for provider \\\"google\\\". Auth store: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json (agentDir: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent). Configure auth for this agent (openclaw agents add <id>) or copy auth-profiles.json from the main agentDir. (auth)\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"cab35f19-abbb-4552-9a4a-8593733afe45\",\n      \"agentId\": \"aparicio\",\n      \"name\": \"📋 Aparício: Ronda das PRs (Merge Diário)\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1771266846233,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1771295805118,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"tz\": \"America/Porto_Velho\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 6 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"TAREFA DE CAPATAZ: Faça a ronda matinal nas Pull Requests.\\n\\n1. Liste as PRs abertas em `adibaldo/adibaldo.github.io` e `franklinbaldo/aparicio-funes`.\\n2. MERGE AUTOMÁTICO (gh pr merge --merge --admin):\\n   - PRs de 'Vitrine', 'Tecedor' e 'Farol' (labels: vitrine, tecedor, seo).\\n   - PRs de boletins ('Mosqueteiro' e 'Pioneiro').\\n3. DEIXAR NO BALCÃO:\\n   - PRs de 'Veritas', 'Prosa' e 'Alfarrabista' (labels: fact-check, prosa, editor).\\n4. Informe ao Franklin o que foi despachado e o que está aguardando o visto.\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1771322400000\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"652cb1b9-9395-45bc-8f1a-1383590f22cc\",\n      \"agentId\": \"aparicio\",\n      \"name\": \"💬 Prosa: Cartografia de Memórias (Daily)\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1771265007681,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1771300800141,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"tz\": \"America/Porto_Velho\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 0 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"export JULES_API_KEY=$(grep JULES_API_KEY /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/secrets.env | cut -d= -f2)\\n\\npython3 /home/franklinbaldo/.op