"wakeMode\":\"now\",\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"Check open PRs on franklinbaldo/causaganha and franklinbaldo/baliza and franklinbaldo/funes-memories using gh CLI. For each repo, list open PRs with: number, title, author, mergeable status. Format as markdown checklist. Write the result to HEARTBEAT.md under the '## 🔔 PRs Pending Review' section (replace that section only). If no PRs, write 'No open PRs.' under the section.\"},\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"none\"},\"state\":{\"nextRunAtMs\":1771313335379,\"lastRunAtMs\":1771309735330,\"lastStatus\":\"error\",\"lastDurationMs\":49,\"consecutiveErrors\":38,\"lastError\":\"Error: All models failed (1): google/gemini-3-flash-preview: Provider google is in cooldown (all profiles unavailable) (rate_limit)\"}},{\"id\":\"3cab287d-3eb9-4946-84c4-5b45edcc1a06\",\"agentId\":\"aparicio\",\"name\":\"memory-sync\",\"enabled\":true,\"createdAtMs\":1771096039127,\"updatedAtMs\":1771309739967,\"schedule\":{\"kind\":\"every\",\"everyMs\":21600000,\"anchorMs\":1771096179772},\"sessionTarget\":\"isolated\",\"wakeMode\":\"now\",\"payload\":{\"message\":\"Execute git sync: git add . && git commit -m 'chore: auto-sync memory' && git push. Ignore 'nothing to commit' errors.\",\"kind\":\"agentTurn\"},\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\"},\"state\":{\"nextRunAtMs\":1771313339967,\"lastRunAtMs\":1771309739847,\"lastStatus\":\"error\",\"lastDurationMs\":120,\"consecutiveErrors\":6,\"lastError\":\"Error: All models failed (1): google/gemini-3-flash-preview: Provider google is in cooldown (all profiles unavailable) (rate_limit)\"}},{\"id\":\"f08d755d-68f7-4bfc-bac5-24f9cd5609f6\",\"agentId\":\"aparicio\",\"name\":\"heartbeat\",\"enabled\":true,\"createdAtMs\":1771017290564,\"updatedAtMs\":1771312490886,\"schedule\":{\"kind\":\"every\",\"everyMs\":1800000,\"anchorMs\":1771017290564},\"sessionTarget\":\"isolated\",\"wakeMode\":\"now\",\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\"},\"state\":{\"nextRunAtMs\":1771314290564,\"lastRunAtMs\":1771312490581,\"lastStatus\":\"error\",\"lastDurationMs\":305,\"consecutiveErrors\":2,\"lastError\":\"FailoverError: No API key found for provider \\\"google\\\". Auth store: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json (agentDir: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent). Configure auth for this agent (openclaw agents add <id>) or copy auth-profiles.json from the main agentDir.\"},\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\"}},{\"id\":\"47eb9367-a34b-433e-9bb6-fb45424543cd\",\"agentId\":\"ireneo\",\"name\":\"Vitrine Funes (SEO Daily)\",\"enabled\":true,\"createdAtMs\":1771263495286,\"updatedAtMs\":1771309460703,\"schedule\":{\"expr\":\"0 9 * * *\",\"kind\":\"cron\"},\"sessionTarget\":\"isolated\",\"wakeMode\":\"now\",\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"Run this exact command to trigger the Vitrine agent via Jules (do not change anything, just run it):\\n\\nexport JULES_API_KEY=$(grep JULES_API_KEY /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/secrets.env | cut -d= -f2)\\n\\npython3 /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/ireneo/workspace/skills/jules-api/jules_client.py create-session \\\\\\n  --source \\\"sources/github/franklinbaldo/funes-memories\\\" \\\\\\n  --title \\\"🪟 Vitrine: Daily SEO Scan\\\" \\\\\\n  --prompt \\\"$(cat /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/ireneo/workspace/memory/bank/jules-agents/vitrine-funes.md)\\\"\\n\\nReport the output JSON (Session ID).\"},\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\"},\"state\":{\"nextRunAtMs\":1771318800000}},{\"id\":\"9e99a605-48d8-4f5a-bde3-67cdeb8fff4e\",\"agentId\":\"aparicio\",\"name\":\"Triagem de PRs do Jules (fork → repo original)\",\"enabled\":true,\"createdAtMs\":1771204172004,\"updatedAtMs\":1771312173244,\"schedule\":{\"kind\":\"every\",\"everyMs\":7200000,\"anchorMs\":1771204172004},\"sessionTarget\":\"isolated\",\"wakeMode\":\"now\",\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"TAREFA: Triagem automática de PRs do Jules no fork do Franklin.\\n\\n1. Rode `gh pr list --repo franklinbaldo/adibaldo.github.io --json number,title,state,createdAt` para listar PRs abertas.\\n2. Se não houver PRs abertas, responda apenas 'Nenhuma PR nova.' e encerre.\\n3. Para cada PR aberta:\\n   a. Rode `gh pr diff <number> --repo franklinbaldo/adibaldo.github.io` para pegar o diff.\\n   b. Analise o diff contra o checklist em memory/diretrizes-editoriais.md seção 4.1.\\n   c. CRITÉRIOS RÍGIDOS:\\n      - Tecedor/Vitrine/Farol (SEO, links, metadados): geralmente OK, mas verificar se não mexem em texto narrativo.\\n      - Veritas (fact-check): REJEITAR se inserir parágrafos novos na prosa do Adi. Só aprovar notas/disclaimers.\\n      - Prosa: NUNCA aprovar edições no miolo narrativo do Adi.\\n      - Tags/description/frontmatter: OK se respeitam a voz original.\\n   d. Se APROVADA: clone o repo original, faça merge da branch (sem force push), push, e feche a PR no fork.\\n   e. Se REJEITADA: deixe aberta e anote o motivo.\\n4. Ao final, envie um resumo ao Franklin dizendo o que foi mergeado e o que foi rejeitado, com os motivos.\",\"model\":\"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5\",\"timeoutSeconds\":300},\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\"},\"state\":{\"nextRunAtMs\":1771319372004,\"lastRunAtMs\":1771312172031,\"lastStatus\":\"error\",\"lastDurationMs\":1213,\"consecutiveErrors\":14,\"lastError\":\"Error: All models failed (2): anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5: No API key found for provider \\\"anthropic\\\". Auth store: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json (agentDir: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent). Configure auth for this agent (openclaw agents add <id>) or copy auth-profiles.json from the main agentDir. (auth) | google/gemini-3-flash-preview: No API key found for provider \\\"google\\\". Auth store: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json (agentDir: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent). Configure auth for this agent (openclaw agents add <id>) or copy auth-profiles.json from the main agentDir. (auth)\"}},{\"id\":\"cab35f19-abbb-4552-9a4a-8593733afe45\",\"agentId\":\"aparicio\",\"name\":\"📋 Aparício: Ronda das PRs (Merge Diário)\",\"enabled\":true,\"createdAtMs\":1771266846233,\"updatedAtMs\":1771295805118,\"schedule\":{\"tz\":\"America/Porto_Velho\",\"expr\":\"0 6 * * *\",\"kind\":\"cron\"},\"sessionTarget\":\"isolated\",\"wakeMode\":\"now\",\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"TAREFA DE CAPATAZ: Faça a ronda matinal nas Pull Requests.\\n\\n1. Liste as PRs abertas em `adibaldo/adibaldo.github.io` e `franklinbaldo/aparicio-funes`.\\n2. MERGE AUTOMÁTICO (gh pr merge --merge --admin):\\n   - PRs de 'Vitrine', 'Tecedor' e 'Farol' (labels: vitrine, tecedor, seo).\\n   - PRs de boletins ('Mosqueteiro' e 'Pioneiro').\\n3. DEIXAR NO BALCÃO:\\n   - PRs de 'Veritas', 'Prosa' e 'Alfarrabista' (labels: fact-check, prosa, editor).\\n4. Informe ao Franklin o que foi despachado e o que está aguardando o visto.\"},\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"announce\"},\"state\":{\"nextRunAtMs\":1771322400000}},{\"id\":\"652cb1b9-9395-45bc-8f1a-1383590f22cc\",\"agentId\":\"aparicio\",\"name\":\"💬 Prosa: Cartografia de Memórias (Daily)\",\"enabled\":true,\"createdAtMs\":1771265007681,\"updatedAtMs\":1771300800141,\"schedule\":{\"tz\":\"America/Porto_Velho\",\"expr\":\"0 0 * * *\",\"kind\":\"cron\"},\"sessionTarget\":\"isolated\",\"wakeMode\":\"now\",\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"export JULES_API_KEY=$(grep JULES_API_KEY /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/secrets.env | cut -d= -f2)\\n\\npython3 /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/aparicio/workspace/skills/jules-api/jules_client.py create-session \\\\\\n  --source \\\"sources/github/franklinbaldo/adibaldo.github.io\\\" \\\\\\n  --title \\\"💬 Prosa: Mapeamento de Memórias\\\" \\\\\\n  --prompt \\\"$(cat /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/apar