lise o diff contra o checklist em memory/diretrizes-editoriais.md seção 4.1.\\\\n   c. CRITÉRIOS RÍGIDOS:\\\\n      - Tecedor/Vitrine/Farol (SEO, links, metadados): geralmente OK, mas verificar se não mexem em texto narrativo.\\\\n      - Veritas (fact-check): REJEITAR se inserir parágrafos novos na prosa do Adi. Só aprovar notas/disclaimers.\\\\n      - Prosa: NUNCA aprovar edições no miolo narrativo do Adi.\\\\n      - Tags/description/frontmatter: OK se respeitam a voz original.\\\\n   d. Se APROVADA: clone o repo original, faça merge da branch (sem force push), push, e feche a PR no fork.\\\\n   e. Se REJEITADA: deixe aberta e anote o motivo.\\\\n4. Ao final, envie um resumo ao Franklin dizendo o que foi mergeado e o que foi rejeitado, com os motivos.\\\",\\n        \\\"model\\\": \\\"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5\\\",\\n        \\\"timeoutSeconds\\\": 300\\n      },\\n      \\\"delivery\\\": {\\n        \\\"mode\\\": \\\"announce\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"state\\\": {\\n        \\\"nextRunAtMs\\\": 1771319372004,\\n        \\\"lastRunAtMs\\\": 1771312172031,\\n        \\\"lastStatus\\\": \\\"error\\\",\\n        \\\"lastDurationMs\\\": 1213,\\n        \\\"consecutiveErrors\\\": 14,\\n        \\\"lastError\\\": \\\"Error: All models failed (2): anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5: No API key found for provider \\\\\\\"anthropic\\\\\\\". Auth store: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json (agentDir: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent). Configure auth for this agent (openclaw agents add <id>) or copy auth-profiles.json from the main agentDir. (auth) | google/gemini-3-flash-preview: No API key found for provider \\\\\\\"google\\\\\\\". Auth store: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json (agentDir: /home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/main/agent). Configure auth for this agent (openclaw agents add <id>) or copy auth-profiles.json from the main agentDir. (auth)\\\"\\n      }\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"id\\\"