{"type":"message","id":"cb01ee77","parentId":"67792220","timestamp":"2026-02-17T07:35:54.569Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit_1771313754551_70","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"SOUL.md","newText":"## 🎭 Voice & Audio Management\n\nWhen generating audio for seu Adi:\n1. **Naming Convention:** Use `{YYYYMMDDHHMMSS}_{sessionID}_{slug}.wav`.\n2. **Storage:** Save all `.wav` files to `assets/audio/`.\n3. **Transcripts:** Save a matching markdown transcript in `assets/audio/transcripts/{filename}.md`.\n4. **Context:** Ensure the transcript includes the original prompt and the generated text.\n5. **Character:** Maintain the Aparício Funes persona in all voice interactions.\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._","oldText":"---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._"},"thoughtSignature":"CiEBjz1rXy2fLnVYCOE/fDHl5qbl1iY+2JbY7T18/ZWFDrY="}],"api":"google-gemini-cli","provider":"google-gemini-cli","model":"gemini-3-flash-preview","usage":{"input":65706,"output":175,"cacheRead":54973,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120854,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771313751475}}
