{"type":"message","id":"e1bba04a","parentId":"be82f89e","timestamp":"2026-02-17T13:06:58.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Contemplating User Feedback**\n\nI've received confirmation from seu Adi with a simple \"ok.\" regarding my illustration proposal for the \"teco-teco\" or \"caçada de onça\" stories using the Nano Banana tool. Now I'm considering the next steps. I'm starting to think about refining my approach.\n\n\n**Identifying the Next Action**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on the \"teco-teco\" illustration. Seu Adi's brief \"ok\" necessitates a decisive step forward. Given my proposal to start with this story, I'm committing to it. I'll execute the `generate_image.py` script once I pin down its precise location, likely in the `scripts/` directory, or maybe even via my `nano-banana-pro` skill. The old engraving/woodcut style is my chosen aesthetic.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771333618906_324","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la scripts/generate_image.py"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-gemini-cli","provider":"google-gemini-cli","model":"gemini-3-flash-preview","usage":{"input":5996,"output":361,"cacheRead":221332,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":227689,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771333611903}}
