{"type":"message","id":"8b481b5d","parentId":"85179332","timestamp":"2026-02-17T14:09:07.560Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"process_1771337347490_574","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":" mesmo sem a gente combinar.\\n-\\n-[Rolim de Moura](/locais/rolim-de-moura/) tem esse jeito: mistura de coragem, poeira, conversa e trabalho. O que eu aprendi ali n\\u00e3o cabe s\\u00f3 em diploma nem em documento \\u2014 cabe em gente.\\n-\\n-Um dia eu conto com mais calma: quem chegou primeiro na minha mem\\u00f3ria foi o som das vozes e o jeito de todo mundo se virar.\\ndiff --git a/src/content/blog/um-ensaio-sobre-o-tempo.md b/src/content/blog/um-ensaio-sobre-o-tempo.md\\ndeleted file mode 100644\\nindex 16f691e..0000000\\n--- a/src/content/blog/um-ensaio-sobre-o-tempo.md\\n+++ /dev/null\\n@@ -1,13 +0,0 @@\\n----\\n-title: \\\"Um ensaio sobre o tempo\\\"\\n-description: \\\"O tempo n\\u00e3o apaga: ele reorganiza. E a gente aprende a ler diferente.\\\"\\n-pubDate: 2026-02-05\\n-tags: [\\\"ensaios\\\", \\\"tempo\\\", \\\"vida\\\", \\\"filosofia\\\"]\\n-heroImage: ./images/ensaio-sobre-o-tempo-cover.png\\n-heroImageAlt: \\\"Imagem abstrata representando a passagem do tempo.\\\"\\n----\\n-O tempo tem duas m\\u00e3os: uma tira, outra devolve.\\n-\\n-Ele tira a pressa (ou pelo menos tenta). E devolve o que a gente n\\u00e3o via quando era novo: detalhe, nuance, cuidado.\\n-\\n-Quando algu\\u00e9m me pergunta por que escrever agora, eu penso que \\u00e9 porque agora eu sei **o que merece ficar**.\\n\",\n              \"baseCommitId\": \"854553d3fc1fd4663cd331d8fe67dcff995ca91c\",\n              \"suggestedCommitMessage\": \"Vitrine: Faxina KonMari e Auditoria SEO\\n\\n- Remo\\u00e7\\u00e3o de posts de exemplo: descobrindo-o-brasil.md, o-cheiro-do-cafe-na-varanda.md, rolim-de-moura-um-comeco.md, um-ensaio-sobre-o-tempo.md.\\n- Remo\\u00e7\\u00e3o da imagem descobrindo-o-brasil-cover.png (as demais imagens j\\u00e1 estavam ausentes).\\n- Cria\\u00e7\\u00e3o de diret\\u00f3rio de logs jules-agents/logs/vitrine/.\\n- Adi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de logs de aprendizado e experi\\u00eancia.\\n- Verifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o de build e auditoria de SEO nos posts restantes.\"\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"id\": \"3f63ba49faa7451eab680afc4d1cf276\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"tide-otter","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"XmFZnR{I`BoPCHHjOHVmB)-9P)vXvN%5rHa~Q-F`fZw}<`B<G`e\\nzuXo%$#3VGvsPR?TDe6E*$o7VSCdY6l$&_`GxF#I9HlrTC6JB@i?K>WHRdCLm*mn%B\\nzga5eanC&{-^2@rcq%88dhbIM78qXA74N_5^w)3ig@^RgxWeT7n#C{3Xo@x#p%3s-u\\nzFN);oQZnkvjtqgmiJqF$P2B4#S7y;y=A53OzCeH7+J9BR^mRll^0+q*;q0uY%uthM\\nz!&~}ewzL4LY4wW#_Dq(9Zx>lGcA@>5JX=|1_3uE>2Xx}lk*wiM_6o+=9OSuju+-a7\\nz7S~}-&c8|ZYsY`ahtS_}CBeU7r}`mc0E&+8^LcGn&HLQ=_^bP`XHT|IV?Hc{i9OpK\\nzm(uI%rmCtEKCCoc+_KMGJ&;F<pH4d^nsCP~{AkOPLIaA$1;*yK_r}LB;j5=3!a@W=\\nzBwZ`&Qn9-xF*<Os=iv1k#XLH;6tLAOvnq0?4<A(BV<!bS>l*=ZjROD^xq2E9AK<Tj\\nz-MLbyZ!i}gazwignoA22hIAA3-D#tvOM7?E1Gb-7#Us@nn{VM>ZU3pN8YX3$6<1Yp\\nz+i)HkA_U6UM_rW4>&&Zi{9S5G2vo8jy&%6VzzWu#&IMZ{fM9)Ka&Z1X)xl|5&NU6y\\nzRiSBxQ}hqY;1>f8z|J*GzkWQ&FF<vO(534BS%>3On@6&h=dVrvma&LJK0hkaFKUw{\\nzI_Yl*PI#9jGnS;H*T*i9hm!)9;-wBya58*qkpo%+kDK@h)uu*qU*QYuqx3xP+&kPH\\nzf}54oo~kF0Mfq@ZUy-;AVAJBQ#^WHUnA=z{KVQU$8hI25>dOY0yU?J1kx~&Ba|!M=\\nz8&6AkSL>xnpYSd3$ghnfDw=E`>}%+F&lY!swAZ{v2*A<S-8Kin?tF1XY+q|?jNHe!\\nzZ^Pet<}AIsCA>{<@!E!WsXvWb2NVRYvw1u1=XeYG-bO7t%Daan@o*-7_!UuIrU^+C\\nzUp5J#%N5mdvn%u=hE?xT>toR3(;pgY`&;{Ot!m#NY<J$&gnY3Kv>Z`Ds%2#ON(QM(\\nz;4^rfx&X%A=YJc@(%HpQNZ8`&*9W(wOmPq@ibv8E?9k|z+a}Fw()F;eDZQCqRF2PZ\\nzQr<QPcbz^+zj$gG((U;ALll(G|4$$F#ex+ET$b3WOqxD%2xGV;PKpF$NrYp=fJno<\\nzKKqj#aybwV35H_-LDC5grWrN{B!Xi4u(7)*-YnK0Fv+-wQB%=l)?zvkl#`WRv)_p7\\nzU8|=@?6PGIf=h=hQ#-UrHc<f5=4-LDdx4148g0W(K3Sz)T;kykcbDW(W)@8lX`CtC\\nz4A5A1SfIfG{#l@y%U0<z&`rQ2sI6!N%py=5t+EA}6HuZb72u_y4SG|}InvB=Qk3t?\\nzkw`)Lm<UBEZF7$(^02ht2m>bl-e{}ihyzULa^`4RvSUXfi|j`nyJr6znGAaZ+Pw*(\\nzNLny2CCsr9Oj-V+TTMX9fB;BqcjJHwU{FIH64}Yf#jrgC7U-}??