{"type":"message","id":"477f72e2","parentId":"9d27405d","timestamp":"2026-02-17T14:18:40.034Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec_1771337919145_598","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"name\": \"sessions/13180824727167331524\",\n  \"title\": \"\\ud83e\\uddf9 Faxineira KonMari: Limpeza de Exemplos\",\n  \"createTime\": \"2026-02-17T14:04:46.214347908Z\",\n  \"updateTime\": \"2026-02-17T14:10:51.230922Z\",\n  \"state\": \"IN_PROGRESS\",\n  \"sourceContext\": {\n    \"source\": \"sources/github/franklinbaldo/adibaldo.github.io\",\n    \"githubRepoContext\": {\n      \"startingBranch\": \"main\"\n    },\n    \"environmentVariablesEnabled\": true\n  },\n  \"prompt\": \"Voc\\u00ea \\u00e9 a KonMari, a arquiteta da ordem no blog Alfarr\\u00e1bios do Adi.\\n\\nMISS\\u00c3O: Limpar o reposit\\u00f3rio de conte\\u00fados de exemplo que n\\u00e3o foram escritos pelo autor real (seu Adi).\\n\\nDIRETRIZES:\\n1. Analise os arquivos em 'src/content/blog/'.\\n2. Identifique arquivos com 'pubDate' anterior a 2026-02-10 (Ex: descobrindo-o-brasil.md, o-cheiro-do-cafe-na-varanda.md, um-ensaio-sobre-o-tempo.md, rolim-de-moura-um-comeco.md).\\n3. Estes s\\u00e3o posts de teste. Agrade\\u00e7a-os pelo servi\\u00e7o e DELETE-os.\\n4. Delete tamb\\u00e9m as imagens correspondentes em 'src/content/blog/images/'.\\n5. Proponha a remo\\u00e7\\u00e3o via Pull Request.\\n\\nVIBE: Serena e minimalista. Deixe apenas o que traz alegria (o conte\\u00fado real do autor).\",\n  \"url\": \"https://jules.google.com/session/13180824727167331524\",\n  \"id\": \"13180824727167331524\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":846,"aggregated":"{\n  \"name\": \"sessions/13180824727167331524\",\n  \"title\": \"\\ud83e\\uddf9 Faxineira KonMari: Limpeza de Exemplos\",\n  \"createTime\": \"2026-02-17T14:04:46.214347908Z\",\n  \"updateTime\": \"2026-02-17T14:10:51.230922Z\",\n  \"state\": \"IN_PROGRESS\",\n  \"sourceContext\": {\n    \"source\": \"sourc